Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:53.90,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:09.00,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,千束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:10.50,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,千束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.09,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,千束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.78,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.58,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.34,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,因為催眠藥 這段時間應該還會很乏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.85,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我被怎麼了嗎 山岸醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.68,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.06,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,因為突然加壓 電池過載
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.73,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再利用軟件控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.86,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也不能再充電了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:43.20,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然簡單 但的確是最直接有效的破壞方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.82,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.37,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那還能撐多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:53.67,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好之前充電了 大概還能撐兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.33,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:58.00,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不亂動 還能堅持更久一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.88,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼叫還能撐兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.17,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.43,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,千束剩下的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.39,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.44,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把壞掉的部分換掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.85,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:20.57,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很不甘心 但是只憑我們的能力什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:26.53,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,千束的人工心臟 沒有替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.70,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.29,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,去殺了那個護士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.21,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.87,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.46,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:41.55,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,本來我就不應該能活那麼長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.76,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,本來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.81,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,就算殺了她也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.81,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.36,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 那個點心不做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.28,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,因為瀧奈知道害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.07,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我都還沒有吃過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.32,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡要一份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.74,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.95,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,瀧奈會生氣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:16.42,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事 顧客就是上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.81,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我是LycoReco咖啡店的美女店員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.56,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,難得你想回DA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.65,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是楠木說有東西給我 非得讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.45,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.95,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.99,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,瀧奈都知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.70,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.42,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才不想告訴她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.50,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是老樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:00.72,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an8}你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.38,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an8}開這麼慢找死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.38,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一群臭小伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.96,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.89,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.73,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,快沒命了 但你還挺精神的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:23.15,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,消息傳得真快啊 所以是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.65,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,重回DA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.57,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我快死了 身體狀況不太合適…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.45,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說真島找過你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.12,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,見過兩次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.41,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你放跑了他兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.83,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那又不是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.79,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這應該是我最後一次來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.63,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,多聊點開心的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.25,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你要給我什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.72,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這個怎麼會在你手上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.72,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,為了防止信息洩露收回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.68,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直找了好久的說 小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:01.19,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上 我們就要展開大規模的討伐真島的作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.61,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.23,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這笑話可不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:10.11,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我們花費了大量的人力物力才把你培養成優秀的莉可麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.45,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,結果你卻要無為而終嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:20.87,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我想的職責和你想的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.21,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒說完 坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.51,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,讓瀧奈回這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.09,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可能考慮下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.51,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 謝謝你還我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.85,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.89,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.15,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,小偷自首了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.77,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.32,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.19,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,點心 點心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.28,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都行 能馬上上的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.95,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,風希你也要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.78,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我們馬上就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.55,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an8}哎 要快點吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.83,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,回復截止明天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.62,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.79,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是讓你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:10.88,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,真島的藏身點找到了 要突破就需要很多戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.63,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,高興了吧 你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.05,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.83,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰在三天後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.26,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an8}哎 等等 風希前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.32,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 打擾您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.31,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,就要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.35,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an8}點心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.35,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎再來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.48,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 瀧奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.90,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:32.11,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不是想回DA嗎 應該表現得更高興一些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.49,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,被笨蛋傳染了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.03,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,好 完事了完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:42.20,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an8\i1}要是完事了就趕緊回來 這裡忙死了趕緊換班…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:42.20,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 哎 嗯 收到 麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:44.73,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,瀧奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.08,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.08,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你後面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.96,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.38,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 還讓你多跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.97,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 那邊那群呢 看好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.55,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦沒事啦 我去收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.10,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.39,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要跑太快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.06,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\an8\c&H4C544D&\frz4.302\org(1508,336)\frx4\fry346\pos(1472,354)}{\fax-0.02}准{\fax-0.03}備{\fax-0.05}中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.82,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你抽煙的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.50,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,要是心裡感受到罪惡了 就會抽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.83,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是給自己一點傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.71,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,要是抽得那麼痛苦 就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:34.92,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我查過了 你早來商量就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.30,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,天才Walnut發現什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.30,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也還束手無策呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.97,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,Alan機關
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.56,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,吉松真司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:48.10,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,網上和他們相關的信息全被抹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.65,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.90,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想直接去問和他們接觸過的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.69,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不太擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:06.21,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,米卡 這都是為了千束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.12,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你也注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:13.21,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,Silent Jin和那個破壞千束心臟的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:17.63,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,幕後黑手都是吉松
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.05,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那是十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是吉先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.31,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.60,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子用槍是殺不了她的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:14.48,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}千束 喂 千束{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.90,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an8\i1}振作一點 千束{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.90,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,她有先天性心臟病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:22.24,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,再過半年 就會死於疾病了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.29,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓這事發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:39.67,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是在ALAN機關幫助下得到的才能的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.59,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人工心臟不會跳動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:50.14,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是遠遠先進於現有技術製成的 最接近實用的一款
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.40,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 也不是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.48,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.11,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,耐久度上有點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:00.65,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,就算用這個也只能堅持到成人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:06.03,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,莉可麗絲的役齡也就十八 能撐到那時候就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.83,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,殺足夠的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:12.37,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是殺人的才能 也能為世人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:16.34,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最重要的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.05,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我就答應你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:26.01,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你也把千束當做殺人道具嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.97,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候變的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.15,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.61,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,米卡 你擅長照顧孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.49,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不太擅長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.82,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明總是被一群孩子圍著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:47.58,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那是工作 要不是我的腳這樣我也不會乾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.41,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 米卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:53.54,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你幫我 在手術後 讓這孩子發揮出她的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:57.33,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 DA會負起責任培養她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.96,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.92,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是已經是我們的女兒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.76,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.47,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次接這種任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.89,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不是任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.81,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是約定 你我之間的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.44,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我說了一些多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:20.73,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 也讓我知道他是什麼樣的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:26.20,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 我和千束的扮家家酒就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.09,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,就是您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.59,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那個救我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.72,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你認錯人了 我只是這裡的員工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:56.14,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 這裡的人不會穿這麼帥氣的西裝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:57.65,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.31,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才應該說謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎麼報答你才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:10.91,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上背負著巨大的使命 好好完成它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.20,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,為此我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.46,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次感覺自己好像救世主一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.21,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.30,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.76,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.39,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,成為救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.11,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.99,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主先生 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.97,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 我怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.64,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不用怕 你馬上就會活蹦亂跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.10,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.98,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.57,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.66,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.29,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,誰給的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.09,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:50.22,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那 這就是能幫助人的槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:57.43,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,真司從那以後就消失了 連我也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.10,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,所以千束才不會殺人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,真諷刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.07,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他們為什麼又要奪走她的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:14.32,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,無功者無命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.41,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣說的話那個護士已經殺掉她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.25,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.92,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,盯著我的那個Alan的人應該也是吉松
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.42,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,真島拿到武器那天應該也是他幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:30.55,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我也能理解真司為什麼要幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:34.51,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到真島 就可以知道千束心臟的信息了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.85,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你都聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.64,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 瑞希也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.39,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用暴露我也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:45.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我們找不到他 從行事誇張的真島入手反而更快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.94,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,能加入到DA的作戰裡就是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.24,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來想拒絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.65,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 你不是很想回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:59.66,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟 這是千束最後的兩個月了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.83,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我會回去DA的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:07.67,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能發現一點讓千束活下去的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.34,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我去和千束說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.21,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 我會自己說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.34,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,請給我時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.39,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.47,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,她說的那個吉先生是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.60,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 不…不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 他是一直幫我們的LAN機關的代理人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.57,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.78,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,Robota 我有個計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.28,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:39.95,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:43.33,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎 嘿歡迎嘿嘿嘿 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.37,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.12,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.33,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.46,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 好閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.21,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.88,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.26,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.18,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.98,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我們出門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.65,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.12,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,第一站是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.79,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你就這樣 不冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.16,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你給我搭的衣服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.75,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這是夏裝啊 你沒有別的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.87,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.59,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:34.92,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我再給你挑一套冬裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.55,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你是一個好模特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.93,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,到時間了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.52,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 還有外套沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.31,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間了 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:59.95,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我們要這麼趕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.20,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.82,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\shad0\fax0.01\fs120\bord0\fnSource Han Sans TC Medium\c&HD3D1D1&\move(516.4,687.4,410.8,605.8,0,3446)\frz7.999}臨時休館通知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.82,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fax0.01\fnSource Han Sans TC Medium\be1\bord0\c&H000000&\frz9.637\move(1321,753.6,1217,670.4,0,3446)}因水槽維修需暫時休館
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.82,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fax0.01\fnSource Han Sans TC Medium\be1\bord0\c&H000000&\frz9.637\move(1114.8,871.4,1009.2,788.2,0,3446)}詳情請查閱官網
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.82,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs60\fax0.01\fnSource Han Sans TC Medium\be1\bord0\c&H000000&\frz10.00\move(1662.2,1006.4,1556.6,921.6,0,3446)}為您帶來不便\N敬請諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.82,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃趕不上變化啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.84,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,好 瀧奈 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:18.55,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,知天命就是我的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.18,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,都釣不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.85,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,釣不上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.81,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.02,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,開心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.10,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.11,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 又到時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.82,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,走了好遠呢 要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:43.99,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.01,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才說你應該穿個外套的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.34,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,也…也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.13,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.30,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.85,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是在等什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.23,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,雪 九點會下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.77,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,本來應該是完美無缺的安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.90,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,神明總是陰晴不定的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.24,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,只有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.78,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.20,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.16,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.62,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你要回DA了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.58,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 太好啦 什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.80,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.26,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你不開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.80,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:46.68,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 的確如果下雪就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.81,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:57.73,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,竟是些不順心的事 你不這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:02.44,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,總是煩惱自己什麼都做不到也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:04.99,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,應該全盤接受 全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.62,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣基本都會帶來好事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:11.20,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你的計劃很成功哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.21,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天玩得很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.75,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.59,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我幹到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.47,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 今天必須回復DA才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:27.80,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.31,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:31.39,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,送別禮啦 拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.02,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.27,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我出發了
