Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:10.81,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}看著你帶來的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:13.98,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}和帶給我的無名之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:16.71,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}今天怎麼還不來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:19.98,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}初次感受到了這種情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:23.57,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}臨摹著裝飾在窗邊的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:26.04,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}獨自在宇宙中玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:31.66,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}本該這樣就足夠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:37.69,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}但一旦握住你手呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:43.77,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}我就很難再次回到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:54.74,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}這不知孤獨的城鎮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:23:00.37,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}你伸出了手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:05.93,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}光明生出了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:08.86,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}唱給我聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:11.68,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}這個故事的後續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:13.57,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}帶我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:20.94,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}直到我們沒有見過的星球
